# 🌐 Digital Career Guidance Platform

A fully responsive **web-based career counseling platform** that helps students discover their ideal academic and professional paths.
It combines **aptitude assessment**, **AI-powered guidance**, and **college exploration tools** — all in one interactive interface.

---

🚀 Features

🧠 Aptitude & Interest Test

* Interactive quiz to identify user’s interests and strengths
* Personalized stream and career recommendations (Science, Commerce, Arts, etc.)

💼 Career Path Explorer

* Comprehensive list of career options with subfields
* Covers multiple streams (Science, Commerce, Arts, Vocational)
🏫 Colleges Directory

* Directory of top **government and private colleges** across Indian states
* Direct **Google Search integration** for more info on fees, courses, and eligibility

🤖 AI-Powered Career Guidance

* Uses **Google Gemini API** to provide intelligent, personalized career counseling
* Supports queries like:

  “What are the best career options after 12th Science?”
  “Which college should I choose for B.Tech in Karnataka?”

🗓️ Timeline & Important Dates

 Academic calendar including board results, exam dates, and admission windows
 Helps students stay organized throughout the admission cycle

 🌌 Beautiful Starry Background & Responsive Design

